  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个设备数据查询的流程图。核心场景是：外部系统通过APIClient发起请求，最终拿到过滤后的设备数据。整个链路要体现云原生的部署形态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。APIClient和DeviceController都是跑在ServiceMesh上的对吧？那DeviceDataFetcher和过滤条件配置呢，部署形态有区别吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DeviceFilterInput"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，APIClient和DeviceController用CloudNative_ServiceMesh。过滤条件DeviceFilterInput和DeviceDataFetcher用HelmChart管理。数据源DataSource是Docker镜像部署的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下流向：APIClient发送过滤输入给DeviceController，Controller用DeviceFilterInput，然后委派给DeviceDataFetcher去数据源查数据。Fetcher把结果返回Controller，Controller再响应给APIClient。这样闭环对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "流程没错。不过DeviceDataFetcher到DataSource的关系要强调一下——是\"applies filters\"，不是简单查询，得体现过滤逻辑下推到数据源这层含义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已更新。现在DataSource节点标注为CloudNative_DockerImage，Fetcher指向它的边写\"applies filters\"。我检查一下其他边的标签。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "DeviceController到DeviceFilterInput的边，我写的是\"uses\"，但你觉得用\"loads config\"会不会更准确？毕竟FilterInput是配置而非运行时依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "\"uses\"更简洁，而且配置加载也属于使用范畴。如果后续有动态重载需求再细化。保持\"uses\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，先保持\"uses\"。另外APIClient到DeviceController的边，我描述的是\"sends filter input\"，这个要保留，体现请求携带过滤参数。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "确认，那条边已标注\"sends filter input\"。现在Fetcher返回结果到Controller，以及Controller最终响应APIClient的两条返回边，标签分别用\"returns results\"和\"responds\"，符合你的习惯吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Fetcher到Controller的\"returns results\"没问题。但Controller到APIClient的\"responds\"会不会太泛？要不要明确是\"returns filtered devices\"？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我试过\"returns filtered devices\"，但和Fetcher那条边语义重复，而且会让APIClient的出边和入边描述不对称。保持\"responds\"更干净，上下文已经能推断是过滤后的结果。我调整回简洁版本。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "同意，简洁优先。整体结构我再确认一遍：六个节点，六条边，部署形态和交互语义都覆盖了。可以定稿。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已定稿。最终布局：APIClient和DeviceController横向排列在ServiceMesh层，DeviceFilterInput和DeviceDataFetcher在HelmChart层，DataSource单独在DockerImage层。所有边标签和部署标注核对无误。",
      "elements_involved": [
